<t>
<field>STATUS</field>
<desc>
            <p>This STATUS field contains one of the following 4 values: </p>
            <p />
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>Status value</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Definition</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Remark</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>Blank</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Automatic</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>The performance was generated automatically by the system.</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>R</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Back-value</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>The performance was recalculated by the system by the back-value process.</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>P</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Purged</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Sub-Case of R  - The Performance should have been recalculated by the back-value process but this has not been done because the corresponding valuation history data was purged in AM.INST.VEH file</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <p>M</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>Manual</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <p>The performance was manually inputted or corrected by the user.</p>
                        <p>The performance was imported from an external file.</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </desc>
</t>
